1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs all internal and external communications during cybersecurity incident response,
 the framework for external partner engagement,
 and the incident response contact directory.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all Information Operations Department personnel participating in or supporting cybersecurity incident response operations,
 and to all communications produced under Chapter 4 authority.
\end_layout

